In CPA marketing, keyword research is one of the most important skills—because your profit depends on targeting people 
at the right intent stage. Let’s break this down in a practical way 👇

🔍 1. How to Do Keyword Research (Step-by-Step)

✅ Step 1: Start with a Base Idea

Pick your niche/product:

Weight loss
Dental implants
Insurance
Skincare

Example: “weight loss supplement”

✅ Step 2: Use Keyword Tools

Use these tools:

Google Trand                 https://trends.google.com/trends/explore?date=today%203-m&geo=US&q=cbd%20oil&hl=en&legacy
https://www.keyword.io/
Google Keyword Planner (Free)
Ubersuggest
Ahrefs
SEMrush

Search your keyword → collect:

Search volume
CPC (very important for CPA)
Keyword variations

✅ Step 3: Check Competitors

Search in Google:

“best weight loss pills”
“buy keto pills”

Look at:

Ads (these are gold 🔥)
Blog articles
Landing pages

✅ Step 4: Use Google Suggestions

Type in Google:

“weight loss p…”
“buy keto…”

Check:

Auto-suggestions
“People also ask”
Related searches

🎯 2. Types of Keywords (VERY IMPORTANT)

There are 3 main keyword types in CPA marketing:

🧠 1. Informational Keywords (Top of Funnel)

👉 User wants information, NOT ready to buy

Examples:
  “how to lose weight fast”
  “what is keto diet”
  “symptoms of diabetes”
  Intent:
  Learning
  Research
  CPA Strategy:
  Blog / Article
  YouTube video
  Collect email

👉 These don’t convert directly but build traffic.

💼 2. Commercial Keywords (Middle of Funnel)

👉 User is comparing options

Examples:
  “best weight loss pills”
  “top keto supplements”
  “review of xyz product”
  
Intent:
  Considering purchase
  Comparing products
  
CPA Strategy:
  Review pages
  Comparison blogs
  “Top 10” articles

👉 These convert better than informational.

💰 3. Buying Keywords (Bottom of Funnel) 🔥

👉 User is READY TO BUY

Examples:
  “buy keto pills”
  “order weight loss supplement online”
  “xyz product price”
  “discount keto pills”
  
Intent:
  Immediate purchase
  
CPA Strategy:
  Direct landing page
  Paid ads (Google/Facebook)

👉 These give highest conversion rate

⚡ 3. How to Identify Keyword Type Quickly
🔎 Look at the words inside keyword:

🧠 Informational Words:
	how
	what
	why
	guide
	tips
	tutorial

👉 Example: “how to lose belly fat”

💼 Commercial Words:
	best
	top
	review
	comparison
	vs

👉 Example: “best keto supplement”

💰 Buying Words:
	buy
	order
	discount
	coupon
	price
	cheap

👉 Example: “buy keto pills online”

📊 4. Pro Tips (VERY IMPORTANT)
✅ High CPC = High Value Keyword

If CPC is high → advertisers are making money → good for CPA

✅ Long-Tail Keywords = EASY PROFIT

Example:

❌ “weight loss”
✅ “best keto pills for women over 30”

👉 Less competition + higher conversion

✅ Spy on Ads

Search on Google → look at ads:

These keywords are already profitable
✅ Match Keyword with Landing Page

  Informational → blog
  Commercial → review page
  Buying → direct offer
  🚀 Simple Real Example

Keyword: “buy dental implants in Bangladesh”

  Type: 💰 Buying keyword
  Strategy: Direct CPA offer / clinic lead form

Keyword: “best dental implant clinic”

  Type: 💼 Commercial
  Strategy: Comparison page

Keyword: “what is dental implant”

  Type: 🧠 Informational
  Strategy: Blog content

  
🔥 Final Strategy (Best for Beginners)
  Target Commercial + Buying keywords    ****
Create:
  Review articles
  Simple landing pages
  Run ads or SEO


  
